{"md5":"916c675bead88815b4f0afbeda634d29","content":"\n\n<p>\n整理gcc下的attribute，避免遗忘。\n</p>\n\n<!--more-->\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-org1f5a925\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org1f5a925\">数据结构</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-org1f5a925\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-orgfe1c77e\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"orgfe1c77e\">结构体非对齐</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-orgfe1c77e\">\n<p>\n在两个系统进行通信发送数据时，经常会要以结构体非对齐方式，以保证数据对应的情况下减小发送带宽。\n</p>\n\n<p>\n使用 <code>__packed</code> 来强制编译器不使用对齐。\n</p>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> __attribute__((__packed__))</span><br><span class=\"line\">{</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">uint8_t</span> cmd;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">uint8_t</span> data;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}cmd_normal;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-orgf5e21fc\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"orgf5e21fc\">消除Warning</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-orgf5e21fc\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org3d1fdf0\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"org3d1fdf0\">指针到整数的转换</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-org3d1fdf0\">\n<p>\nc编程中经常会将指针强制转换为整数以传递地址，但这种情况下gcc会有对应警告，相应的应对解决方案:\n</p>\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>cast from pointer to integer of different size : 将指针强制转换为整数</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">pragma</span> GCC diagnostic push</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">pragma</span> GCC diagnostic ignored <span class=\"string\">\"-Wpointer-to-int-cast\"</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//强制转换代码放这里</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">pragma</span> GCC diagnostic pop</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>cast to pointer from integer of different size : 将整数强制转换为指针</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">pragma</span> GCC diagnostic push</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">pragma</span> GCC diagnostic ignored <span class=\"string\">\"-Wint-to-pointer-cast\"</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//强制转换代码放这里</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">pragma</span> GCC diagnostic pop</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\nLast Updated 2018-07-26 四 21:35.<br>Render by <a href=\"https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-renderer-org\">hexo-renderer-org</a> with <a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/\">Emacs</a> 25.3.1 (<a href=\"https://orgmode.org\">Org</a> mode 9.1.13)\n"}
